Kwiyongera byihuse kw'ibyago by'indwara ya Coronavirus (COVID-19) mu muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Afurika y'Ubukungu n'Ubwongereza, kuva ku itariki ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Umubare w'abanduye Coronavirus (COVID-19) ugaragara mu bihugu by'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi /Afurika y'ubukungu n'u Bwongereza, wonyine wagiye wiyongera mu bihugu byose, nubwo icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri mu cyiciro gitandukanye bitewe n'igihugu.
Dushingiye ku byo twabonye mu Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bafite COVID-19 bigomba kurushaho kwitegura umubare munini w'abarwayi bazaba bakeneye kwitabwaho mu by'ubuvuzi, cyane cyane mu by'ubuvuzi bukomeye.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, hari itsinda ry'abantu barwaye indwara y'ibihaha bataramenya aho baba, mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari icyorezo cya coronavirus, ubu cyitwa coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 yiswe indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19).
Ibimenyetso kugeza ubu ni uko abagera kuri 80% by'abantu bafite COVID-19 bafite indwara yoroheje, ni ukuvuga ubwandu bw'inzira zo guhumeka zifite cyangwa zitagira ubumuga bw'ibihaha, kandi abenshi muri bo barakira.
Mu bantu bagera kuri 14%, COVID-19 ihinduka indwara ikomeye cyane igasaba kujya mu bitaro, mu gihe abandi 6% bahura n'indwara ikomeye igasaba kwitabwaho cyane.
Umubare w'abarwayi bapfa bajyanywe mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 ni hafi 4%.
Muri iki cyigisho, tugereranya imiterere y'icyorezo cya COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cy'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/icyanya cy'ubukungu cy'u Burayi (EU/EEA) no mu Bwongereza (Ubwongereza) maze tugereranye n'icy'intara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Nanone dugereranya umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 muri EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza n'uw'u Butaliyani ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama15 Werurwe 2020.
Abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Afurika y'iburasirazuba n'u Bwongereza
Nyuma y'u Bushinwa, COVID-19 yakwirakwijwe mu by'ubutaka kandi imbaraga z'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bindi bice by'isi muri iki gihe zikurikirana iz'iki gihugu.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu nomero yo ku wa 5 Werurwe 2020 ya Eurosurveillance, Spiteri et al. yatangaje ku bantu ba mbere b'i Burayi bemejwe ko banduye COVID-19 nk'uko bigaragara mu gisobanuro cy'ibyabaye na OMS.
Mu karere ka EU/EEA, abantu batatu ba mbere banduye bavuzwe n'Ubufaransa ku wa 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bagarutse bavuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020, hari hamaze kugaragara abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu byose 30 by'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'Uburayi / EEA no mu Bwongereza (Ubwongereza), aho hagati y'itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 n'uwo munsi, habayeho abantu 39,768 bapfuye, naho mu Butaliyani honyine hapfuye abantu 17,750.
Kubona umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 hamwe n'ibyababayeho
Mu Kigo cy'Igihugu cy'Igihugu cy'Igihugu cy'Igihugu gishinzwe Gukurikirana no Gukurikirana Indwara (ECDC), imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 batangajwe mu bihugu byose ku isi, iboneka mu makuru y'ibiro by'igihugu gusa, urugero nk'ibiro by'Ubuzima, inzego z'ubuzima z'ibihugu n'ibihugu ndetse n'umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima (WHO), ihora ihererekanywa buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gupima imikorere ya COVID-19 muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, no kuyereranya n'iy'u Butaliyani.
Nk'ikimenyetso cy'ibyongereye mu bantu banduye COVID-19, twagerageje kugenzura iminsi 14 y'ibyongereye mu bantu banduye COVID-19, bityo tukita ku buryo bwa kamere bwa COVID-19, mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, mu gihe cy'itariki ya 1 Mutarama15 Werurwe 2020.
Twagaragaje kandi umubare w'abantu bahuye n'ikibazo cyafashwe n'iki kibazo ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani za mu gitondo ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama15 Werurwe 2020.
