Ibipimo by'iminsi 14 by'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza muri rusange byakurikiye ibya Hubei Province (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza muri rusange, ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwatangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, hanyuma bwazamutse cyane ahagana ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Ibindi bintu).
Ibi ahanini byatewe n'umubare w'abanduye uvuye mu Butaliyani wiyongereye cyane, ariko ibindi bihugu byose bya EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza byagaragaje ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wiyongereye cyane (Ibintu by'inyongera).
Ishusho ya 2 yerekana umubare w'abanduye COVID-19, mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani ku wa 31 Mutarama15 Werurwe 2020.
Ryerekana ko ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani za mu gitondo, ibindi bihugu 15 byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Afurika y'iburasirazuba n'u Bwongereza byari byaravuze umubare w'abanduye ugereranywa n'uwa u Butaliyani, hashize ibyumweru bitatu gusa cyangwa mbere yaho.
Ibisubizo byacu bigaragaza ko umubare w'abamaze kumenyekana ko banduye COVID-19 wiyongera cyane muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibipimo by'icyorezo cya COVID-19 bigaragara ko kigenda gitera imbere mu bihugu byose ku muvuduko ungana n'uwo.
Ibi ni ukubera ko ibihugu biri mu byiciro bitandukanye, hari ibyahindutse mu buryo abaturage bakiriye ubuzima bw'abaturage, ndetse hari n'imiterere itandukanye y'ibimenyetso mu bihugu ndetse n'amabwiriza atandukanye yo guhitamo abarwayi bagomba gupimwa kugira ngo bagaragaze ko banduye COVID-19, harimo no gupima guhita bagerwaho.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere twatewe n'iki cyorezo mu Butaliyani basobanuye imimerere aho abagera kuri 10% by'abarwayi bafite COVID-19 basabwaga kwitabwaho cyane, kandi ibitangazamakuru byatangaje ko ibitaro n'ibigo byitabwaho cyane muri utwo turere byari bimaze kugera ku bushobozi bwabyo busesuye.
Kugeza ubu amakuru ku bantu bemerewe kujya mu bitaro no mu kigo cyita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 ku rwego rwa EU/EEA, ku bantu 6% gusa na 1% gusa (amakuru ntiyaragaragajwe).
Icyakora, ibyo byagombye gutorwa mu buryo bufatika kugira ngo bigeze ku makuru y'ubugenzuzi ahari, yibanda ku mubare w'abamaze kuvugwa n'umubare w'abapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-11 bwagaragaje ko mu Burayi hari ibitanda by'uburwayi bwo mu rwego rwo kwivuza cyane n'iby'uburwayi bwo mu rwego rwo hagati bihari, kuva ku mitanda 29.2 mu Budage kugeza ku mitanda 4.2 ku baturage 100.000 muri Porutugali.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bishobora kugira umutungo munini cyangwa munini ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (12,5 ibitanda byo kwita ku bantu bari mu bitaro by'ubuvuzi bukomeye n'iby'ubuvuzi hagati ku baturage 100.000 mu 201011).
Imyiteguro y'ibyagereranywa bijyanye no guhaza ubushobozi bwo kwita ku buzima, hamwe n'ibipimo by'igihugu cya EU / EEA na UK by'ibimenyetso by'abanduye COVID-19 bajyanywe mu bitaro bifitwe isano n'igihungabana cya 90% cyo kurenga ubushobozi bw'ibitanda byo kwita ku buzima busanzwe, bitangwa mu cyiciro cya gatandatu cy'igihungabana ry'ibyago byihutirwa bya ECDC kuri COVID-19.
Kubera ko kugeza ubu abarwayi bagiye bakorakoranywa mu turere tumwe na tumwe two mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bukomeye bigakorera abaturage b'akarere runaka, amakuru ku babarwayi n'ibitaro by'ubuvuzi bukomeye agomba kuboneka mu cyiciro cya 2 cy'ibipimo by'ubwandu (NUTS-2).
Ubuhanga bw'u Butaliyani n'imikorere y'ubu mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri gutera imbere mu buryo bwihuse mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bafite uburwayi bukomeye, bityo bigomba kwitegura ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora gukwirakwira mu baturage kandi umubare w'abarwayi bafite COVID-19 ukagenda wiyongera, bakaba bakeneye kwitabwaho mu buryo bw'ubuzima, cyane cyane mu gihe hari uburwayi bukomeye, nk'ubwo buboneka mu turere twugarijwe n'iyo ndwara mu Butaliyani.
Nkuko byagaragajwe mu isuzuma ry'ibyago rya ECDC riherutse gukorwa, uburyo bwihuse, bwagutse kandi bufite ireme ni ngombwa kugira ngo kwandura kwa SARS-COV-2 bihagarare, hakagira n'ubwo guhinduka kuva ku buryo bwo kugabanya ubwandu ku buryo bwo kugabanya ubwandu, kuko kwiyongera kwa vuba kwitezwe kw'umubare w'abanduye bishobora gutuma abategura ibyemezo n'ibitaro badahabwa igihe gihagije cyo gusobanukirwa, kwemera no guhindura uko bitwara mu gihe kitaragera.
Igereranya ry'akaga mu buryo bwihuse kandi ryerekana ingamba z'ubuzima bwa rubanda zo kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Hariho uburyo bugufi ibihugu bifite bwo kongera imbaraga mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya ingufu ku buvuzi.
Iyo ibyo bitabaye, birashoboka ko mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru bizaba bizaba, gahunda z'ubuvuzi mu bindi bihugu by'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA zizagira umubare munini w'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho mu buryo bukomeye.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe na coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kugeza ubu kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3,000, cyandura abarenga 80,000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, bigatera impanuka ku bantu.
Kimwe na virusi yayo y'ubwoko bumwe, SARS-CoV, yateje SARS ku bantu ibihumbi mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 nayo ishobora kwandura mu mikungugu kandi igatera ibimenyetso nk'ibyo binyuze mu buryo nk'ubwo.
Ariko kandi, COVID-19 ifite ubukana n'ubwandu buke ugereranyije na SARS ariko ni bwo bwandura cyane kandi bugira ingaruka ku bantu bakuze kurusha abakiri bato ndetse n'abagabo benshi kurusha abagore.
Kubera ko hari ibitabo byinshi bivuga iby'iyo ndwara, iyi ngingo igamije gutanga ibisobanuro ku birebana n'icyo kibazo cy'ubushakashatsi kigiye kigenda gihinduka mu buryo bwihuse.
Tuzasuzuma ibintu by'ibanze ku birebana n'indwara, indwara z'abantu, virusi, indwara, uburyo bwo kuvurwa, ibipimo by'indwara n'uburyo bwo kwirinda iyo ndwara.
Nubwo ibibazo byinshi bikiriho bisaba ibisubizo, twizeye ko iki gice kizafasha gusobanukirwa indwara ishobora guteza akaga kandi ikayirandura burundu.
Umunsi mukuru w'Icyumweru ku wa 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye urwibutso rutazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose basabwe kuguma mu nzu mu gihe cyose cy'iminsi mikuru no mu byumweru byinshi nyuma yaho kubera icyorezo cy'indwara nshya y'umugera.
Iyi virusi ni imwe cyane na coronavirus (CoV) yateje icyorezo cya SARS mu mwaka wa 2003; bityo, yashyizweho izina rya SARS-CoV-2 n'umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima (WHO) ku wa 11 Gashyantare 2020, kandi indwara ifitanye isano na yo yiswe COVID-19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, maze kiza gukwirakwira mu gihugu hose, kigera ku bandi bagera kuri 50 ku isi hose.
Ku itariki ya 2 Werurwe 2020, iyi virusi imaze gutuma habaho abantu barenga 80,000 banduye COVID-19, abarenga 40,000 barekuwe ndetse abarenga 3,000 barapfa.
OMS iragabisha ko COVID-19 ari umwanzi w'abaturage wa 1 kandi ko ishobora kuba ikomeye kurusha iterabwoba.
PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), ivuga ko mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, hasohotse ibitabo birenga 200 ku COVID-19 birimo virusi, icyorezo, indwara, indwara n'ubuvuzi kuva raporo ya mbere yo ku wa 7 Mutarama 2020 yagaragaje uko virusi yagendaga yihererana ku barwayi benshi.
Muri iyi ngingo, hagaragaramo uko ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu gice gishya kandi kiri mu iterambere mu buryo bwihuse.
Igihe cyose bishoboka, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara iterwa na CoV, indwara yo mu mwuka yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS, icyorezo cyatangiye mu 2012).
Nanone tuzasuzuma ibyo tumaze kumenya ku birebana n'uburyo bwo kwirinda iyo ndwara no kuyivura, ndetse n'ibibazo bimwe na bimwe bikiriho ariko byihutirwa.
Ubusanzwe, abantu babona ko ko virusi itera ibicurane ari ubwandu butera indwara, cyane cyane iyo ari yo ituma abantu bagera kuri 15% bahura n'indwara z'ibicurane.
Icyakora, muri iki kinyejana, twahuye na COVID y'abantu ifite ubwandu bw'indwara inshuro ebyiri, ni ukuvuga SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, byateje icyorezo mu Bushinwa mu 2003 no muri Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, kandi bidatinze byakwirakwiriye mu bindi bihugu byinshi bifite ubwandu buteye ubwoba n'ubwandu bw'abantu bapfa.
Ku bw'ibyo, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya COVIDV mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragara ku ishusho ya Fig.1,1, amaterasi y'uburwayi bw'ibihaha yari afite inkomoko itamenyekanye yabanje kuvugwa i Wuhan ku wa 31 Ukuboza 2019 kuri Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Igihugu y'u Bushinwa.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, icyorezo cya CoV cyasohotse.
Tariki ya 15 Mutarama 2020 nibwo havuzwe icyorezo cya mbere cy'urupfu cyaturutse i Wuhan.
Hagati aho, icyo cyorezo cyarakwiriye mu migi, mu ntara no mu bihugu byari bituranye.
Ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama, abantu batangaga ubuvuzi batangajwe ko banduye, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko umuntu ashobora kwandura indwara.
Ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan warafunze, imodoka zose za rusange zihagarara.
Ku itariki ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe ku ndwara bwagaragaje ko ku barwayi 41 banduye, 21 gusa ari bo bari bafitanye isano ya bugufi n'isoko ry'ibyokurya byo mu nyanja rya Wuhan, aho ubwandu bwavuye ku nyamaswa zitamenyekanye.
Ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari icyihutirwa ku isi hose.
