Hari abarwayi bagaragaje ko bafite indwara yo guhumeka no guhumeka mu maso (dyspnea) cyangwa ko bafite hypoxémie nyuma y'icyumweru kimwe bamaze kurwara.
Mu gihe cy'ibiza, abarwayi bahise bagira indwara yo mu buryo bw'umwuka, indwara yo guturika kw'amaraso, indwara ya acidosis mu mubiri no kugira indwara yo mu bwonko.
Abarwayi bafite umuriro n'imyanya y'ubuhumekero n'umuriro ukaze, ndetse n'abatarwaye indwara z'ibimenyetso by'ibinyabuzima, bagomba gusuzumwa kugira ngo bashobore kubona virusi mu gihe cya mbere.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019 bwagaragaje ko umubare w'abarwaye indwara z'indwara z'indwara z'ubushyuhe wari 98% ku ndwara y'ubushyuhe, 76% ku ndwara y'ubushyuhe bwumye, 55% ku ndwara y'ihindagurika ry'amaraso, na 3% ku ndwara y'uruhu; 8% by'abarwayi basabwaga guhumeka.
Ibimenyetso nk'ibyo byatangajwe mu bushakashatsi bubiri buherutse gukorwa ku muryango n'ubundi bushakashatsi bwagaragajwe n'umuntu udafite ibimenyetso.
Mu buryo buhuje n'ubwo, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2012 bwagaragaje ko abarwayi ba MERS-CoV na bo bari bafite umuriro (98%), ubuhumekero bwumutse (47%), no guhumeka (55%) nk'ibimenyetso byabo by'ibanze.
Ariko 80% by'abo bantu bari bakeneye ubufasha bwo guhumeka, birenze cyane abarwayi ba COVID-19 kandi bihuje n'ubwandu bw'indwara ya MERS kurusha COVID-19.
Mu barwayi ba MERS, na bo bagaragaye indwara yo kuvura (26%) n'ububabare bw'umujinya (21%).
Mu barwayi ba SARS, byagaragajwe ko umuriro (99%-100%), gusohoka kw'umwotsi (29%-75%), dyspnea (40%-42%), isahane (20-25%) n'ububabare bw'umugongo (13-25%) ari byo bimenyetso bikomeye kandi ko inkunga yo guhumeka yari ikenewe ku barwayi bagera kuri 14%-20%.
Ku itariki ya 14 Gashyantare, umubare w'abapfa bahitanywe na COVID-19 wari 2% ubwo abanduye bemerwaga ku isi bose bageraga ku 66,576.
