Akenshi, iyo umuntu atangiye gukora ingendo mu matsinda, aba ari mu muryango umwe cyangwa ari mu nzu imwe cyangwa imodoka imwe, urugero nk'ubwato bw'ingenzi.
Abarwayi bakunze kuba bafite amateka y'ingendo cyangwa kuba mu mujyi wa Wuhan cyangwa mu tundi duce twatewe n'iyo ndwara cyangwa guhura n'abantu banduye cyangwa abarwayi mu byumweru bibiri bishize mbere y'uko iyo ndwara itangira.
