Muri ibyo bikorwa harimo imiti ikoreshwa muri iki gihe n'iyo ishobora gukoreshwa mu gihe kiri imbere, urugero nk'imiti irwanya virusi, imiti itera ubwirinzi, imiti itera ubukana bw'umubiri, ibiyobyabwenge bifasha umubiri, ibiyobyabwenge byo mu bwoko bw'amaraso by'abarwayi bongeye gukira, imiti y'Abashinwa n'ubufasha bwo mu mutwe.
