Ku itariki ya 6 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ryacu ryasohoye amabwiriza yihutirwa yo gusuzuma no kuvura icyorezo cya coronavirus (2019-nCoV) cyo mu mwaka wa 2019, kandi aya mabwiriza yatumye tugira ubumenyi kandi agaragaza neza uko kurwanya iki cyorezo ku isi hose.
Icyakora, icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) ni indwara nshya, ubumenyi bwacu n'ubumenyi bwacu biragenda byiyongera buhoro buhoro bishingiye ku bushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ubunararibonye mu buvuzi; bityo rero, ingamba zo gusuzuma no kuvura na zo ziracyavugururwa.
Muri iyi baruwa, twasubije ikiganiro kimwe ku buyobozi bwacu kandi dutanga ibipimo bishya byo gupima abashidikanyaho  n'abashidikanyaho  nk'uko bigaragara mu mabwiriza ya vuba aha yo gupima no kuvura COVID-19 (gitabo cya karindwi) yashyizweho na Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika y'Abaturage y'u Bushinwa.
Mu Ukuboza 2019, Coronavirus nshya ya 2019 (2019-nCoV) yatumye habaho icyorezo, ubu cyiswe ku mugaragaro Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19) kandi virusi yiswe Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020, OMS yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2, itsinda ryacu ryakoze amabwiriza yihutirwa kandi yashyizwe ahagaragara kuri interineti mu kinyamakuru cya Military Medical Research ku wa 06 Gashyantare 2020.
Kuva cyasohoka, cyakiriwe n'abantu benshi.
Ariko kandi, zirikana ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, ubumenyi bwacu n'ubumenyi bwacu bigenda byiyongera buhoro buhoro bishingiye ku bushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa no ku byaranze ubuvuzi; bityo rero, ingamba zo gusuzuma no kuvura na zo zirahinduka buri gihe.
Urugero, Amabwiriza yo gupima no kuvura COVID-19 yashyizwe ahagaragara na Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika y'u Bushinwa (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), hagati ya 16 Mutarama 2020 kugeza tariki 3 Werurwe 2020, yashyizwe ahagaragara muri rusange inshuro zirindwi, aho hari ibintu byahindutse cyane.
Ubu ubuyobozi bwacu bwahawe ibitekerezo na Zhou et al., bashyizeho igitekerezo cyoroshye cyo gutanga amanota hashingiwe ku byo bagezeho mu buvuzi.
Umurimo wabo wongeyeho ibimenyetso bishya ku buyobozi bwacu kandi kandi ni igihamya cy'agaciro kuri iki cyorezo ku isi hose.
Dushimira umurimo wabo w'ingenzi.
Ariko kandi, ibikorwa byabo na byo bikeneye kuvugururwa ukurikije Amabwiriza ya vuba y'Ibarura no Kuvura COVID-19 (Icyiciro cya karindwi cy'igeragezwa) n'ubushakashatsi buheruka gukorwa.
