Amateka y'icyorezo: (1) amateka y'ingendo cyangwa ubwenegihugu mu mujyi wa Wuhan n'uturere tuwukikije, cyangwa mu bindi bihugu aho habayeho abantu banduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira; (2) amateka y'imibonano n'abantu banduye SARS-CoV-2 (bafite ikizamini cya asidi ya nucleic); (3) amateka y'imibonano n'abarwayi bafite umuriro cyangwa ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan n'uturere tuwukikije, cyangwa mu bindi bihugu aho COVID-19 yari imaze kubonwa mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira; (4) amateka y'imibonano n'abantu benshi bemejwe (≥ 2 banduye umuriro n'ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero byabereye mu byumweru 2 mu bice bito, nko mu rugo, mu biro, mu ishuri, n'ibindi).
Ibimenyetso bya muganga: (1) umuriro n'ibimenyetso byo guhumeka; (2) ibimenyetso byo kwifotoza ubwandu bwa COVID-19; (3) imibare yose y'ingirabuzima fatizo z'amaraso igaragaza ko imibare y'ingirabuzima fatizo zisanzwe, yagabanutse cyangwa yagabanutse mu ntangiriro.
Gusuzuma icyorezo cyemejwe byagombye gushingira ku cyorezo kigikekwaho kimwe mu bimenyetso by'ubwandu cyangwa ibimenyetso bya serolojiya nk'ibi bikurikira: (1) ikigeragezo cya PCR mu gihe nyacyo cyashimishije SARS-CoV-2; (2) urutonde rw'ubwoko bwose bwa virusi rugaragaza ko ari rumwe cyane n'ubwandu bwa coronaviruses nshya izwi; (3) cyashimishije IgM yihariye n'igisi ya IgG kuri SARS-CoV-2 mu kigeragezo cya serum; cyangwa guhindura IgG yihariye ya SARS-CoV-2 kuva ku itagira akamaro ikajya ku cyiza, cyangwa igitero cy'igisi cya IgG kizamuka inshuro ≥4 mu gihe cyo gukira kirenze icyo mu gihe cyo gukira.
