Ku wa kane, umubare w'abanduye Coronavirus ya SARS-CoV-2 warenze miliyoni ku isi hose, nk'uko byagaragajwe n'amakuru ya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins.
Abantu bagera ku bihumbi 52 bapfuye bazira COVID-19, indwara yatewe na coronavirus.
Iki gikorwa cyabaye ku munsi umwe Malawi yemeje ko imaze kwandura Coronavirus bwa mbere ndetse na Zambia ikaba yarapfuye bwa mbere kubera Coronavirus.
Koreya ya Ruguru yavuze ko ku wa kane ari kimwe mu bihugu bike bikiriho bitanduye Coronavirus.
