Amazu y'ubucuruzi yo muri Ositaraliya ashyiraho imipaka yo kugabanya ibiciro by'ibitabo by'ubwiherero ku gicuruzwa
Ku cyumweru no ku wa gatandatu nimugoroba, amaduka yo muri Australia yitwa Woolworths na Coles yagabanyije ibihano byo kugura impapuro z'icyumba cyo mu bwiherero ku mpande ebyiri n'imwe ku gicuruzwa kimwe mu maduka yose ku rwego rw'igihugu, hakurikijwe.
ALDI na yo yashyizeho imipaka y'ibikoresho by'ubushake bumwe, ku wa mbere.
Ibi bihano byashyizwe mu butumwa ku ma kaseti, no ku mapaji ya Facebook y'amakete.
Bivugwa ko abaguzi bari bafite ibikoresho byinshi kubera ubwoba bwa COVID-19 mu gihe abantu baba bakeneye kwigunga.
Ku wa Gatatu, Woolworths yananiwe kugura impapuro z'icyumba cyo gukoreramo imirimo yo mu rugo, igera ku giceri kimwe ku cyiciro.
Ibi bihinduka byaje nyuma y'ibikoresho bine bya mbere by'ubucuruzi byashyizweho na Woolworths na Coles ku itariki ya 4 na 5 Werurwe.
Coles, mu itangazo ryayo ryo ku wa 8 Werurwe, yatangaje ko kubera ko hari ibicuruzwa bine byatangiye gucuruzwa, "amaduka menshi aracyakomeje kugurishwa mu isaha imwe nyuma yo gutanga", maze avuga ko ibyo asabwa "bitigeze bibaho", mu gihe ALDI, mu nyandiko yo kuri Facebook kuri uyu wa Kabiri, yavuze ko "bitari bitezwe".
Umuvugizi wa Woolworths yavuze ko mu cyumweru gishize, ibicuruzwa byazamutse cyane.
Ubucuruzi bwa Costco i Canberra na bwo bwagabanyije umubare w'amafaranga yemerewe mu cyumweru gishize ku byumba bibiri.
Kugira ngo ikibazo cy'ubukene gikomeze kwiyongera, Coles yategetse ko abaguzi batanga ibyokurya byinshi kandi ko buri gihe batanga ibicuruzwa byinshi, Woolworths na yo itanga ibyokurya byinshi, naho ALDI igatanga ibyokurya ku munsi wa gatatu wari wateganyijwe.
Russell Zimmerman, umuyobozi mukuru w'Ishyirahamwe ry'Abakozi bo mu Bushinwa Batanga Imodoka, yavuze ko abacuruzi bagerageza kongera umubare w'ibicuruzwa, ariko ko abayobozi b'uturere bahagaritse igihe cyo gutanga amatike bigatuma ibintu bibagora.
Atekereza ko ibiciro by'ubucuruzi bizagenda byiyongera, kuko abaguzi bazajya bagerageza guhangana n'ibisabwa, kandi ko ibicuruzwa bidasanzwe bizaba bike.
Ku wa Kabiri, ALDI yatangaje ko nyuma yo gutanga ibikoresho hakiri kare, amaduka amwe n'amwe atashobora gutangiza ibirori byo ku wa Gatatu.
Mu nkuru yo kuri News.com.au, Dr Gary Mortimer, umuhanga mu by'ubucuruzi wo muri Queensland University of Technology, yavuze ko amaduka yuzuza ibyo bintu buri joro.
Yavuze ko impapuro z'icyuma ari ibintu byinshi, bigatuma umubare w'ibikoresho biboneka ari muke, kandi iyo byamaze kugurishwa, bituma ibigega byinshi biba bitagira icyo bigeraho, bigatuma umuntu yumva ko hari icyo bimukeneye.
Russell Zimmerman wavuze kuri ABC News ati "Abagize umuryango wa Coles na Woolworth babona ko iyo haboneka ibintu byinshi ku gasheluzo, kandi ko hari ibintu byinshi bishobora kugurwa, urugero nk'ibikoresho by'ubwiherero n'ibikoresho bifasha gusuzuma isuku, ushobora kugabanya ubwoba".
Umukozi ukora imyanda y'ibikoresho by'isuku yavuze ko ku wa Gatatu w'icyumweru gishize nta bicuruzwa byari bikiriho.
Kimberly-Clark, ikora Kleenex Toilet Tissue, na Solaris Paper ikora Sorbent, bashimangiye ko bakora amasaha 24 kuri 24 kugira ngo bakomeze kubona ibyo batanga, nk'uko raporo ya News.com.au ibigaragaza.
Domain.com, ikigo cy'ubucuruzi bw'ibinyabuzima, cyatangaje ko abacuruzi bamwe batangaga impapuro z'icyumba cy'isuku ku buntu ku muntu wa mbere watangaga ibiciro mu cyamunara i Melbourne, ubwo cyakoraga cyamunara nke kubera ko abaguzi bari bafite igihe cyo kuruhuka mu mpera z'icyumweru kirekire ku munsi w'abakozi.
Igazeti yo ku wa kane ya NT News, ari yo gazeti y'iminsi yose yasohokaga i Darwin, yari irimo inyandiko y'amapaji umunani yagombaga gutemwa maze ikagirwa nk'impapuro z'icyuma.
Muri iyi nkuru yo ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe, ABC Australia yatangaje ko ibigo by'ubucuruzi bitashakaga gushyiraho ibihano ku byo bicuruza.
Russell Zimmerman yongeyeho ko hari n'ibindi bicuruzwa bicyari mu byo gukoreshwa cyane, harimo udupfukamunwa, imiti ihumura, ibicuruzwa byumye, gukaraba intoki n'umuceri.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, hanze ya Ositaraliya, ku cyumweru nimugoroba ku isoko rikuru ryo mu Bwongereza rya Ocado ryabonetse ku rubuga rwa interineti, ryagombaga kugura impapuro z'icyuma z'isuku za Andres mu macupa abiri gusa.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo
Ku wa Gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateye Coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 ari icyorezo.
Nubwo ijambo "icyorezo" ryerekeza gusa ku kuntu indwara yandutse mu rugero rwagutse, aho kwerekeza ku kuntu abantu bamwe na bamwe bafite akaga, OMS yavuze ko ari ngombwa ko leta zitera inkunga yo kugira icyo zikora:
"Ibihugu byose biracyabasha guhindura uko iki cyorezo cyagenze.
Iyo ibihugu byiboneye, bigerageza, bivura, bigata, bikagenzura, bikagenzura kandi bikagira uruhare mu guhangana n'ibi bibazo", ni ko Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS yavuze.
"Turi impungenge cyane ku rugero rubabaje rw'icyorezo n'ukuntu cyakwirakwiriye, ndetse n'ukuntu abantu batagira icyo bakora".
Dr. Tom Frieden wahoze ari umuyobozi w'Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika Gishinzwe Kurinda no Kurinda Indwara, yavuze ko icyo cyorezo "kitazwiho".
Yavuze ko mu magambo CNN yasohoye muri Gashyantare, "utari uruzi rw'ibicurane, nta wundi virusi yo mu buryo bw'ubuhumekero yakurikiranwe kuva yatangira kugeza ikwirakwira ku isi hose".
Ghebreyesus yagaragaje igitekerezo nk'icyo, avuga ko "nta kindi gihe twigeze tubona icyorezo cyatewe na coronavirus".
Yakomeje agira ati "nta kindi gihe twigeze tubona icyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa icyarimwe".
Icyorezo gishya cyiswe icyorezo gikurikiye icyemezo cya OMS cyo gutangaza ko iki cyorezo ari icyihutirwa mu buzima bwa rubanda ku rwego mpuzamahanga.
Umuyobozi w'Ikigo cy'Amerika Gishinzwe Indwara z'Amatwara n'indwara zandura, Dr. Anthony Fauci, yavuze ko iyo ndwara "izarushaho kuba mbi".
Kugeza kuwa kane, Associated Press yatangaje ko ku isi hose hari nibura abantu 126,000 banduye COVID-19, bigatuma hapfa abantu barenga 4.600.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 201920 ni icyorezo gikomeje cy'indwara ya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe n'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero ya coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Iki cyorezo cyagaragaye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa mu Ukuboza 2019, cyatangajwe nk'icyorezo cy'indwara y'uburwayi mpuzamahanga ku wa 30 Mutarama 2020, cyemezwa nk'icyorezo ku wa 11 Werurwe 2020.
Ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 1.61 banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu 210 n'uturere, bituma abantu bagera ku 97.000 bapfa.
Abantu bagera ku 364.000 barakize.
Umubare w'abapfa ufatwa n'abantu benshi mu Bushinwa ugereranyije ni 4%, mu gihe ku isi hose uri hagati ya 13.04% muri Algeria na 0.08% muri Nouvelle Zélande.
Mu bimenyetso bikunze kugaragara harimo umuriro, gusuka no guhumeka nabi.
Mu bibazo bishobora kuvuka harimo indwara y'ibihaha n'indwara y'ubuhumekero.
Igihe kuva umuntu agaragaye ibimenyetso bikimara kumvikana, akenshi kiba iminsi igera kuri itanu, ariko gishobora kuba kiri hagati y'iminsi ibiri n'umunani.
Nta nkingo cyangwa imiti yihariye ya virusi bizwiho.
Uburyo bw'ibanze bwo kuvurwa ni ubuvuzi bufite ibimenyetso kandi bufasha.Ibintu by'ubudahangarwa bihanuriwe birimo gukaraba intoki, guhisha umunwa igihe umuntu ashonje, gukomeza gutandukana n'abandi bantu, no gukurikirana no kwiherera ku bantu bakeka ko banduye.
Abayobozi bo hirya no hino ku isi bagiye bashyiraho amategeko agenga ingendo, gushyira mu kato abantu, gushyiraho amasaha y'akazi, kugenzura akaga kari mu kazi no gufunga ibigo.
Iki cyorezo cyatumye ku isi hose haba ibibazo bikomeye mu bukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage, imyidagaduro, ibikorwa by'idini, ibya politiki n'iby'umuco bigatinda kubera ko abantu batinya kugura ibintu, ndetse n'ibicuruzwa byinshi bikomeje kubura.
Amashuri n'amashuri makuru byafunzwe mu bihugu 193 haba mu gihugu hose cyangwa mu karere, bigira ingaruka ku bantu bagera kuri 99,4 ku ijana by'abanyeshuri bo ku isi.
Amakuru atari yo ku byerekeye iyi virusi yagiye akwirakwira kuri interineti, kandi habayeho ibikorwa byo gukunda abanyamahanga no kubarobanura ku butoni ku baturage bo mu Bushinwa, abandi baturage bakomoka mu Burasirazuba no mu Majyepfo y'Iburasirazuba bwa Aziya, n'abandi baturutse mu turere tubarimo abantu benshi banduye iyi virusi.
Kubera ko ingendo zigabanutse n'inganda zikomeye zifunze, umwuka wahumanyijwe n'umwuka wa CO2 wagabanutse.
Ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa (umurwa mukuru w'intara ya Hubei) bwatangaje ko ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 habayeho icyorezo cy'indwara z'ibihaha zitamenyekanye, kandi iperereza ryatangiye mu ntangiriro za Mutarama 2020.
Abenshi mu bantu bagaragaye ko bafite isano n'isoko ry'ibikomoka ku mazi rya Huanan, bityo bivugwa ko iyi virusi ifite inkomoko ya zoonotic.
Virusi yatumye iki cyorezo cyandura izwi nka SARS-CoV-2, virusi iherutse kuvumburwa ifitanye isano ya bugufi na coronaviruses ya bat, coronaviruses ya pangolin, na SARS-CoV. Umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanye ufite ibimenyetso yaje kuvumburwa ko yarwaye ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019, kandi uwo muntu nta sano rigaragara yari afite n'agatsiko k'isoko ririmo imvura y'amazi.
Mu bantu ba mbere bavuzwe mu Ukuboza 2019, bibiri bya gatatu byabonetse ko bifitanye isano n'isoko.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe 2020, raporo itari yemewe y'ikinyamakuru cya South China Morning Post yagaragaje ko hari umuntu w'imyaka 55 wo mu ntara ya Hubei washoboraga kuba ariwe wa mbere wanduye iki cyorezo ku itariki ya 17 Ugushyingo 2019. Ku itariki ya 26 Gashyantare 2020, OMS yatangaje ko kubera ko abarwayi bashya bagaragaye ko baguye mu Bushinwa ariko bagabanutse mu buryo butunguranye mu Butaliyani, Irani na Koreya y'Epfo, umubare w'abarwayi bashya hanze y'u Bushinwa warenze umubare w'abarwayi bashya mu Bushinwa ku ncuro ya mbere.
Hari igihe abantu batagira icyo bavuga ku ndwara, cyane cyane mu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje.
Ku itariki ya 26 Gashyantare, hari abantu bake cyane banduye mu rubyiruko, abo bantu 19 bari munsi y'imyaka 2,4% y'abanduye ku isi. Umujyanama mukuru w'ubumenyi w'Ubwongereza, Patrick Vallance, yavuze ko 60% by'abaturage b'u Bwongereza bagomba kwandura mbere y'uko ubwirinzi bw'umukumbi bushoboka.
Ibimenyetso by'abanduye ni umubare w'abantu bageragejwe COVID-19, kandi ibizamini byabo byemejwe ko ari byiza nk'uko byemejwe n'amategeko.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyarakoze ibizamini by'abantu barenga 3% by'abatuye isi, kandi ibihugu byinshi byagize politiki y'ubutegetsi yo kudakora ibizamini ku bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje gusa, urugero nk'u Butaliyani, u Buholandi, Esipanye n'Ubuswise.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku wa 16 Werurwe bwagaragaje ko mu Bushinwa, kugeza ku wa 23 Mutarama, abagera kuri 86% by'abanduye COVID-19 bataraboneka, kandi ko izi ndwara zitanditse ari zo zateye 79% by'abanduye.
Mu isesengura ry'imibare ryasohowe ku wa 30 Werurwe, hagaragajwe ko umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani wari munini cyane ugereranyije n'abamaze kuvugwa.
Ingero z'ibanze z'umubare w'ibanze w'abanduye (R0) ba COVID-19 zari 1.4 kugeza 2.4.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'Ikigo cya Amerika Gishinzwe Kurinda no Gukumira Indwara, bwagaragaje ko ishobora kuba ari 5.7.
Abantu benshi bafite COVID-19 barakira.
Ku bantu badafite ibimenyetso, igihe cy'ibimenyetso kugeza bapfuye cyari hagati y'iminsi 6 na 41, kandi icy'ingenzi ni iminsi 14.
Ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera ku 97,000 bapfuye kubera COVID-19.
Mu Bushinwa, ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, abagera kuri 80% by'abapfuye bari mu bafite imyaka isaga 60, naho 75% bari bafite ibibazo by'ubuzima byariho mbere harimo indwara z'umutima n'indwara ya diyabete.Ibipimo by'abapfuye ku bw'icyorezo cya COVID-19 muri rusange byerekeza ku bapfuye bagaragaye ko banduye COVID nk'uko byemejwe n'amategeko.
Umubare w'abapfa mu by'ukuri bahitanywe na COVID-19 ushobora kuba ari munini cyane, kuko ushobora kutaba ugizwe n'abapfa batabanje gupimwa - urugero nko mu rugo, mu bigo by'abakecuru, n'ibindi.
Amakuru amwe n'amwe yo mu Butaliyani agaragaza ko umubare w'abapfuye mu gihe cy'icyorezo urenze umubare w'abapfuye ku COVID ku buryo bwagaragaye inshuro 4-5 ku mubare w'abapfuye ku butegetsi.
Umuvugizi w'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) yemeye ko " tuzi ko [umubare w'abapfuye wavuzwe] ari ugupfobya", itangazo ryemezwa n'inkuru z'ibyabaye ku bantu batagira umubare muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika.
Urupfu rwa mbere hanze y'u Bushinwa rwabaye ku itariki ya 1 Gashyantare muri Filipine, naho urwa mbere hanze ya Aziya rwabaye mu Bufaransa ku itariki ya 14 Gashyantare.
Ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, hari abantu barenga 12 bapfuye mu bihugu bitandukanye, harimo u Bushinwa, Koreya y'Epfo n'u Butaliyani.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, ibihugu birenga mirongo ine n'ibisagara byari byaravuze ko abantu bapfuye, ku mugabane wose uretse Antarctica.
Ibipimo by'abapfuye bihinduka bitewe n'akarere n'igihe, kandi bigerwaho n'umubare w'abapfuye bagabanwa n'umubare w'abarwayi bagaragaye mu gihe runaka.
Hashingiwe ku bipimo bya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins, igipimo cy'abapfuye ku isi ku giti cyabo ni 6.0% (97.039/1.617.204) ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020.
Umubare w'abantu ugenda utandukana bitewe n'akarere.
Mu Bushinwa, ibipimo by'abapfa ku bantu bapfa byagabanutse kuva kuri 17.3% (ku bafite ibimenyetso byatangira tariki ya 1-10 Mutarama 2020) kugera kuri 0.7% (ku bafite ibimenyetso byatangira tariki ya 1 Gashyantare 2020).Ibindi byiciro birimo umubare w'abapfa ku bantu bapfa bazize indwara (CFR), igaragaza umubare w'abapfa bazize indwara, n'umubare w'abapfa ku bantu bapfa ku ndwara (IFR), igaragaza umubare w'abafite indwara (bafite indwara n'abatarazi) bapfa bazize indwara.
Aya makuru ntabwo agenga igihe kandi akurikirana umubare runaka w'abantu kuva ku ndwara kugeza ku guhangana n'ikibazo cy'indwara.
Hari intiti nyinshi zagerageje kubara iyo mibare ku bantu runaka.
Ikigo cya Kaminuza ya Oxford gishinzwe ubuvuzi bushingiye ku bimenyetso gitangaza ko umubare w'abandura bahitanwa n'icyorezo muri rusange uri hagati ya 0.1% na 0.39%.
Igitekerezo cyo hejuru cy'iki gitangazamakuru gihuye n'ibyavuye mu igeragezwa rya mbere ry'ikoranabuhanga rya COVID-19 mu Budage, n'igikorwa cy'ubushakashatsi bw'imibare gisesengura ingaruka z'igeragezwa ku gitekerezo cya CFR.
OMS ivuga ko icyorezo gishobora gukoreshwa.
Igihe cy'ikirenga n'igihe cy'imperuka cy'icyorezo ntibiramenyekana kandi bishobora gutandukana bitewe n'aho kibereye.
Maciej Boni wo muri kaminuza ya Pennsylvania yagize ati "Iyo indwara idahari, akenshi iba itaratangira gukwirakwira, ariko iyo indwara igeze ku bantu benshi, igatangira kwiyongera.
Ariko muri iki gihe, biragoye cyane kumenya igihe ibyo bizabera".
Umujyanama mukuru mu by'ubuvuzi wa leta y'u Bushinwa, Zhong Nanshan, yavuze ko "bishobora kurangira muri Kamena" niba ibihugu byose bishobora gushishikarizwa gukurikiza inama za OMS ku ngamba zo guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, Adam Kucharski wo mu Ishuri ry'Ubuzima n'Ubuvuzi bw'Ibihe by'Ikirere ry'i Londres yatangaje ko SARS-CoV-2 "izagenda igenda igenda igenda igenda igenda igenda, ishobora kumara umwaka cyangwa ibiri".
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Neil Ferguson mu kigo cy'amashuri ya Imperial College, bwagaragaje ko hakenewe kwirinda abantu ku buryo bw'umubiri n'ibindi bintu "kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rufite ubushobozi bwo kuboneka (hashobora kuba hashize amezi 18 cyangwa arenga)".
William Schaffner wo muri kaminuza ya Vanderbilt yagize ati "Ntekereza ko bitashoboka ko iyi coronaviruskuko ishobora kwandura cyaneizashira burundu" kandi"ishobora guhinduka indwara y'ibihe, igasubizwaho buri mwaka".
Kugira ngo uwo muntu agaruke mu buryo bw'umwuka bizaterwa n'uko afite ubwirinzi mu mukumbi n'uko avuka.
Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba bitamenyekanye cyane kandi abantu banduye bashobora kuba badafite ibimenyetso.
Ibimenyetso bibiri bikunze kugaragara ni umuriro (88%) n'igihu cyumye (68%).
Mu bimenyetso bikunze kugaragara gake harimo umunaniro, guhumeka, gutakaza ibyokunywa, guhumeka nabi, imitsi n'ububabare bw'imyanya y'ubuvungukira, kuribwa n'umujinya, umutwe, guhinda umushyitsi, kuvira, ihumeka, isesemi cyangwa se indwara y'ibicurane.
Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyanditse ibimenyetso by'impanuka nk'ububabare bwo guhumeka, kubabara cyangwa kumanikwa mu gituza, guhungabana mu buryo butunguranye, gukorana no kubyuka, no kurakara kw'amaso cyangwa iminwa; inama yo guhita ihabwa ubuvuzi mu gihe ibyo bimenyetso biriho.Igihe indwara ikomeza gutera, bishobora gutuma umuntu agira indwara ikomeye y'ibihaha, indwara yo guhumeka nabi, sepsis, icyibuha cy'amaraso n'urupfu.
Bamwe mu banduye bashobora kuba badafite ibimenyetso, nta bimenyetso bya muganga bafite ariko bakaba bafite ibizamini byemeza ko banduye, bityo abashakashatsi batanze inama y'uko abantu bagiranye isano rya bugufi n'abantu banduye bagombye gukurikiranwa neza kandi bakagenzurwa kugira ngo birinde ko bagwa mu ndwara.
Abashinwa bavuga ko umubare w'abandura indwara z'indwara utari ufite ibimenyetso, uri hagati ya 44 na 44%.
Igihe gisanzwe cyo kuryamana (igihe gihuza ubwandu n'imiterere y'ibimenyetso) gitangira iminsi imwe kugeza kuri 14; ubusanzwe ni iminsi itanu. Nk'urugero rw'uburangare, ingero y'abantu barwaye COVID-19 batakaje ibyokunywa bya mbere yari 30% nyuma yaho igabanuka igera kuri 15%.
Hari ibintu bimwe na bimwe birebana n'uko iyo ndwara ikwirakwira bikomeje kumenyekana.
Iyo ndwara ishobora gukwirakwira cyane cyane iyo umuntu afitanye na yo imishyikirano ya bugufi, cyangwa iyo umuntu afashwe n'ibitonyanga bito by'amazi igihe ashonje, ashonje cyangwa avuze.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko iyo umuntu atagaragaje ko ashuha, ashobora guterwa n'ibitonyanga bigera kuri metero 15 kugeza kuri metero 8.2.
Hari abavuze ko virusi ishobora no kwandura binyuze mu bitonyanga bito biguma mu kirere igihe kirekire, bishobora kuvuka mu gihe cy'ijambo.
Ayo matovu ashobora kugera mu kanwa cyangwa mu mazuru y'abantu baba hafi aho cyangwa se akaba ashobora guhumeka mu mahaha.
