Abaganga umunani muri bo, harimo na Li Wenliang, bakosowe n'igipolisi kubera ko bakwirakwizaga ibinyoma, naho undi witwa Ai Fen, yakosowe n'abayobozi be kubera ko yavugaga ko hari ibintu bitari byo.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Wuhan nyuma yaho yashyize ahagaragara itangazo ku wa 31 Ukuboza maze ibimenyesha OMS.
Abategetsi b'ubuzima b'i Wuhan bari barabonye amakuru ahagije y'ibyago by'uburwayi butamenyekanye, kugira ngo hatangire iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama.Mu bihe bya mbere by'icyorezo, umubare w'abanduye wikubye kabiri buri minsi irindwi n'igice.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020, virusi yageze mu zindi ntara z'u Bushinwa, ifashijwe n'impunzi z'umwaka mushya w'u Bushinwa ndetse n'aho Wuhan ari ihuriro ry'ingendo n'ubucuruzi bukomeye bw'umuriro.
Ku wa 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwavuze ko mu munsi umwe honyine habayeho abantu bashya bagera ku 140, barimo abantu babiri i Beijing n'umwe i Shenzhen.
Amakuru y'ubutegetsi nyuma agaragaza ko abantu 6.174 bari bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso ku wa 20 Mutarama 2020.Ku wa 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zarushijeho gutwara Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani ku isi umubare munini w'abanduye.Ku wa 9 Mata 2020, ku isi hose hamaze kuvugwa abarwayi basaga miliyoni 1.61; abantu basaga 97.000 barapfuye abandi basaga 364.000 barakira.
Ibihugu bigera kuri 200 n'uturere twaho byiboneye nibura umuntu umwe urwaye indwara.
Kubera icyorezo cyugarije u Burayi, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen byagabanyije ubwisanzure bwo gutembera no gushyiraho ibipimo by'ingamba ku mipaka.
Mu bitekerezo by'igihugu harimo ingamba zo kwirinda abantu, urugero nko kuba mu kato (zwi nka gahunda yo kuguma mu rugo, gutaha cyangwa gufunga) n'ibihano byo gutaha.Ku wa 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 300, cyangwa 90% by'abaturage, bari mu buryo runaka bafunze muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, abantu barenga miriyoni 50 bari muri Guma mu rugo muri Filipine, abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 59 bari muri Guma mu rugo muri Afurika y'Epfo, naho abantu miliyari 1.3 bari muri Guma mu Rugo mu Buhinde.
Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi bari mu bwoko runaka bwo gufunga, iki cyongereye ku bantu miliyari 2.6 nyuma y'iminsi ibiri, ni ukuvuga kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wanduye COVID-19 yemejwe ko ari iya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan; raporo imwe itarakemezwa igaragaza ko umuntu wa mbere wanduye COVID-19 ari iya 17 Ugushyingo.
Dogiteri Zhang Jixian yabonye icyorezo cy'indwara z'ibihaha ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, aho ibitaro bye byamenyesheje Wuhan Jianghan CDC ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza.
Igerageza rya mbere ry'ubwoko bw'abarwayi ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza 2019 ryerekanye ko hari coronavirus isa na SARS.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Wuhan yasohotse itangazo rusange ku wa 31 Ukuboza.
OMS yamenyeshejwe kuri uwo munsi.
Ubwo ibi byatangazwaga, abaganga bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan baburiwe n'igipolisi ko "bakwirakwiza ibihuha" ku byerekeye iki cyorezo.
Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima mu Bushinwa yabanje kuvuga ko nta "bihamya bifatika" bigaragaza ko umuntu ashobora kwandura indwara.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije ubukangurambaga bw'inkomoko, nyuma yaho buvugwa na Xi Jinping, umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti ryo mu Bushinwa, ko ari "intambara y'abaturage" yo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Mu cyiswe "ikigo kinini cyo kwirinda abantu mu mateka y'abantu", ku wa 23 Mutarama hatangajwe ko hari gahunda yo guhagarika ingendo zo kwinjira no kuva mu mujyi wa Wuhan, kandi ko cyongerewe kugera mu mijyi 15 muri Hubei, bigatuma abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 57 baba mu gihugu.
Mu mujyi imodoka z'abikorera zari zibuzanyijwe.
Mu duce twinshi, kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa (ku itariki ya 25 Mutarama) byarahagaritswe.
Abayobozi batangaje kandi ko hari kubaka ibitaro by'agateganyo, ibitaro bya Huoshenshan, bikaba byarangiye mu minsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, hubatswe indi bitaro, ari byo bitaro bya Leishenshan, kugira ngo bifate abandi barwayi.
Uretse ibitaro bishya byubatswe, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bigo 14 byo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, urugero nk'ibigo by'amakoraniro n'ibibuga by'imikino, bikaba ibitaro by'agateganyo.Ku wa 26 Mutarama, guverinoma yashyizeho izindi ngamba zo guhashya icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutanga ibyangombwa by'ubuzima ku bagenzi no kwagura ikiruhuko cy'umunsi mukuru w'Itangiriro.
Kaminuza n'amashuri hirya no hino mu gihugu na byo byafunzwe.
Akarere ka Hong Kong na Macau kafashe ingamba zitandukanye, cyane cyane ku mashuri n'amashuri makuru.
Mu turere tumwe na tumwe two mu Bushinwa hashyizweho ingamba zo gukora ku buryo bwa kure.
Ibihano byo kujya mu mahanga no mu mahanga byashyizweho.
Imodoka zitwara abantu mu ruhame zarashyizwe mu bikorwa, maze inzu ndangamurage zo mu Bushinwa zose zifungwa by'agateganyo.
Mu mijyi myinshi hakoreshejwe ingendo z'abaturage, kandi hagaragajwe ko abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bahanganye n'ingamba zo kugabanya ingendo mu rugo.Igihe icyorezo cyatangiye ku rwego rw'isi muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'u Bushinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda ko virusi "yiva mu bindi bihugu".
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho iminsi 14 yo gushyira mu kato abanyamahanga bose binjira mu mujyi.Ku wa 23 Werurwe, Ubushinwa bw'ibanze bwari bwanduye umuntu umwe gusa mu minsi itanu yari ishize, muri iki gihe binyuze ku munyururu wasubiye i Guangzhou avuye i Istanbul.
Ku itariki ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'u Bushinwa Li Keqiang yatangaje ko gukwirakwira kw'abanduye mu gihugu hagati kwahagaritswe mu buryo bw'ibanze kandi ko icyorezo cyagenzurwa mu Bushinwa.
Kuri uwo munsi, ibihano byo kujya mu bihugu bitandukanye by'u Bushinwa byagabanyutse mu mujyi wa Hubei, uretse mu mujyi wa Wuhan, nyuma y'amezi abiri itegeko ryo gufunga ryatangiye. Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'u Bushinwa yatangaje ku wa 26 Werurwe 2020 ko kwinjira ku bafite viza cyangwa uruhushya rwo kuba mu Bushinwa bizamuzwa ku wa 28 Werurwe, nta makuru asobanutse neza azajya ahagaragara ku gihe iyo politiki izarangira.
Abafite ubushake bwo kwinjira mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba viza muri ambasade cyangwa muri za konsulatiri z'u Bushinwa.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yashishikarije ubucuruzi n'inganda kongera gufungura ku wa 30 Werurwe, kandi itanga inguzanyo z'amafaranga ku bigo.Inama y'Igihugu yatangaje umunsi wo kurira ku itariki ya 10 tariki ya 4 Mata, ku munota wa 10 w'iminota itatu, uhuriye n'umunsi mukuru wa Qingming, nubwo leta nkuru yasabye imiryango guha icyubahiro kuri interineti mu kubahiriza ibanga ry'umubiri kugira ngo birinde icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyongera kwibasira.
COVID-19 yemejwe ko yageze muri Koreya y'Epfo ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020 ivuye mu Bushinwa.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ko ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare habayeho kwiyongera kw'abanduye, ahanini bikaba byatewe n'iteraniro ry'umutwe mushya w'idini uzwi ku izina rya Shincheonji Church of Jesus i Daegu.
Abari mu idini rya Shincheonji bari baje i Daegu baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan, bakekwaho ko ari bo batangije iki cyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bayoboke 9,336 b'itorero, 1,261 cyangwa 13% bavuze ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko ku itariki ya 23 Gashyantare 2020 ari ho hari umutekano wiyongereye cyane.
Ku wa 28 Gashyantare, abanduye barenga 2000 bamaze kwemezwa muri Koreya, biyongeraho 3,150 ku wa 29 Gashyantare.
Inzu zose za gisirikare za Koreya y'Epfo zahagaritswe nyuma y'uko ibizamini byemeje ko abasirikare batatu banduye iyi virusi.
Amatariki y'indege na yo yarahuye n'ingaruka kandi ni yo mpamvu yahindutse. Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho gahunda yafashwe nk'iyikomeye kandi iteganijwe neza kurusha izindi ku isi yo gupima abaturage kugira ngo barinde virusi, no kwiherera abantu bose banduye ndetse no gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abahuye na bo.
Uburyo bwo gupima bwarimo gutanga raporo y'ibimenyetso by'abashya baje mu mahanga binyuze mu porogaramu ya terefone, gupima virusi ku buryo bw'imodoka ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima kugirango abantu bagera ku 20,000 bashobore gupimwa buri munsi.
Igihugu cya Koreya y'Epfo gifatwa nk'igikorwa cyatsinze mu kurwanya iki cyorezo nubwo kitashyize mu kato imijyi yose.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba ko Moon ashinjwa ibyo bavuga ko ari amakosa ya leta mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo, cyangwa se bashima uko yabyitabiriye.
Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Koreya y'Epfo ifite umubare muto w'abanduye umunsi umwe mu byumweru bine.
Ku itariki ya 29 Werurwe, hatangajwe ko guhera ku itariki ya 1 Mata, abantu bose bashya bavuye mu mahanga bazajya mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri.
Amakuru atangwa n'itangazamakuru ku itariki ya 1 Mata, avuga ko Koreya y'Epfo imaze kubona ibisabwa byo gufashwa mu gupima virusi mu bihugu 121 bitandukanye.
Irani yatangaje ko ku itariki ya 19 Gashyantare i Qom, ari ho habonetse abantu ba mbere banduye SARS-CoV-2, aho Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi yatangaje ko abantu babiri bapfuye nyuma y'uwo munsi.
Mu ngamba za mbere leta yatangaje harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, imikino n'amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, no gufunga za kaminuza, ibigo by'amashuri yisumbuye n'amashuri.
Irani yashyize hanze miliyari eshanu z'amafaranga y'u Rwanda kugira ngo irwanye iyi virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ku wa 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato imijyi yahuye n'iki cyorezo, kandi ko abantu bonyine ari bo bazajya mu kato.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, hatangajwe gahunda yo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imigi, nubwo ingendo nyinshi hagati y'imigi mbere y'Umwaka mushya wa Nowruz wa Peresi zakomeje.
Ibibanza by'Abashiya i Qom byatangiye kubakwa ku bahetamye kugeza ku wa 16 Werurwe 2020.Igihugu cya Iran cyabaye icyicaro cy'icyorezo cya Virusi nyuma y'u Bushinwa muri Gashyantare.
Mu gihe hari abivuga ko hari abantu bahishe ubukana bw'iki cyorezo muri Irani, ibihugu birenga icumi byari byashyize ibimenyetso by'ibyabaye muri Irani ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko ubukana bw'iki cyorezo bushobora kuba bukomeye kurusha abanduye 388 Leta ya Irani yatangaje kuri uwo munsi.
Inteko Ishinga Amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe, kandi 23 mu banyamuryango bayo 290 bavuga ko bagaragaye ko banduye virusi ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe.
Ku itariki ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye abayobozi ba gereza za Irani kurekura mu buryo butaziguye abashinzwe uburenganzira bwa muntu bafungiwe mu nzira y'amahoro, ndetse no kurekura by'agateganyo imfungwa zose zifite uburenganzira bwo kurekurwa.
Yavuze ko hari ibyago byinshi by'uko virusi ikwirakwira mu bigo bifunze nka za gereza, aho na zo zidafite ubuvuzi bukwiye.
