Gukaraba intoki buri gihe ukoresheje isabune mu "minsi y'ingenzi" y'umunsi bifasha kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'umuriro n'indwara ya kolera, zishobora kwandura mu kanwa.
