Impamvu y'ibanze ikoreshwa mu buvuzi mu gukaraba intoki, ni ukwirinda indwara ziterwa n'ibyorezo (bakiteriya, virusi cyangwa izindi ndwara zishobora gutera indwara) n'ibikomoka ku bintu bishobora guteza indwara.
