Iyo myifatire yoroheje ishobora kugabanya abantu bapfa bazize izo ndwara hafi 50%.
Gukurikiza gahunda yo gukaraba intoki bishobora kugabanya ibice bitatu by'abafite ikibazo cy'uruhererekane rw'amaraso, ibyo bikaba bisa n'aho umuntu yabikora mu duce tudafite amikoro make.
48% by'ibyago byo kurwara indwara y'uruhu bishobora kwiyongera bitewe no gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni bwo buryo bwonyine bwonyine bworoshye kandi bw'igiciro gito bwo kwirinda uruhu n'indwara zihitana mu buryo bw'ubuhumekero (ARI), kuko imyitwarire ikorwa mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu baturage ku isi hose.
