Ibikoresho bifasha guhanagura ubwandu mu kunywa inzoga bica uturemangingo, uturemangingo tw'ubwoko bwinshi tw'imiti (MRSA na VRE), igituntu, hamwe na virusi zimwe na zimwe (harimo virusi itera SIDA, herpes, RSV, rhinovirus, vaccinia, grippe na hépatite) n'ibishyimbo.
