Mu mwaka wa 2008, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Kaminuza ya Westminster, mu mujyi wa Londres, kandi buyobowe n'abikorera mu by'amapine, ni bwo bwashyizweho mu rwego rw'itsinda ry'abantu bo mu Burayi (European Tissue Symposium), kugira ngo bagereranye uburyo bwo gukora neza mu gihe umuntu afite isuku, imashini zo gutunganya intoki zikorana umwuka ushyushye n'imashini zo gutunganya intoki zikorana umwuka ushyushye.
