Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki, habonetse impinduka zikurikira mu mibare y'udukoko:
Hariho abahanga benshi bakora imashini zo gutunganya amafunguro, kandi bagereranyije imashini zo gutunganya amafunguro n'impu.
Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje imyenda yo kwisiga intoki ni uburyo bwiza bwo kubigeraho mu gihe ugiye mu ngendo, mu gihe nta sabuni cyangwa amazi.
