Nyuma y'igihe kirekire Ignaz Semmelweis, umuganga w'Umuhungari, abonye ko gukaraba intoki ari ngombwa mu buvuzi (mu wa 1846) byatumye umuntu arwara indwara mu bitaro.
Hari ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki bifasha abakozi bo mu bitaro kwibuka ko bagomba gukaraba intoki mu gihe bibagiwe.
Hari ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko iyo bakoresheje izo ndwara, umubare w'abandura uba ugabanutse.
