Amaboko yagombye guhanagurwa hamwe n'ibimenyetso by'ibimenyetso.
Niba hari ibisigazwa biri munsi y'imisumari, ushobora kubikuraho ukoresheje igishura.
Kubera ko mikorobe zishobora kuguma mu mazi ku biganza, ni iby'ingenzi ko ubyuhagira neza kandi ukabihanagura ukoresheje igishura gisanzwe.
Nyuma yo gukama, igikoresho cy'urukozasoni kigomba gukoreshwa kugira ngo amazi avemo (kandi niba ari ngombwa, ukingure urugi rusohoka).
Ibyo birinda ko amaboko yongera kwanduzwa n'ibyo bintu.
Guhanagura intoki mu kigo cy'ubuvuzi bigamije gukuraho uturemangingo duto dutera indwara (abagereranywa n'udukoko) no kwirinda ko dutwara.
Hari ikinyamakuru cyavuze ko mu bihugu byinshi usanga gukaraba intoki bitemewe, kandi ko abaganga benshi n'abaforomokazi bakunze kwibagirwa gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukorakora ku barwayi, bityo bakaba bashobora kwandura uturemangingo.
Hari ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki mu buryo bukwiriye n'ibindi bikorwa byoroheje bishobora kugabanya umubare w'indwara zo mu maraso ziva ku ntoki z'umuntu zigera kuri 66 ku ijana.
Igitabo cy'ubuyobozi bw'umuryango ku bijyanye n'isuku y'amaboko gishobora no kuboneka ku rubuga rwawo rw'ikoranabuhanga kugira ngo abantu bose babyibaze.
Isuzuma rihuje n'ibyo ryakozwe na Whitby et al.
Ibikoresho by'ubucuruzi bishobora gupima no kwemeza isuku y'amaboko, niba bisaba kugaragaza ko amategeko yubahirizwa.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye Ryita ku Buzima rifite "iminota itanu" yo gukaraba intoki:
nyuma yo kwanduzwa n'amaraso/imiyoboro y'umubiri
mbere yo gukora akazi k'ubushakashatsi, kandi
Nyuma yo kwita ku barwayi.Kwongeramo imiti itera indwara mu myanya y'ubuhumekero (myanda y'ubuhumekero cyangwa imiti y'ubuhumekero) bituma umukozi wo gukaraba intoki agira ingaruka mbi.
Kugira ngo umuntu 'akoreshe' intoki ze mu gihe cy'ubuvuzi, agomba kugira umwambi ushobora gukoreshwa kandi ukamugaruka atagombye kuwukoresha, umwambi wa chlorhexidine cyangwa iodine, imyambaro idasembuye yo gukaraba intoki nyuma yo kuyikaraba, n'ikime cyo gukaraba n'ikindi gikoresho kidasembuye cyo gukaraba munsi y'imisumari.
Ibintu byose by'amabara byagombye kuvanwaho.
Muri iyo nzira, umuntu agomba gukaraba intoki n'amaboko kugeza ku nkokora, akenshi mu gihe cy'iminota 26.
Si ngombwa ko umuntu ahita ahanagura amazi mu gihe kirekire (iminota 10).
Iyo ukeneye gukaraba, ugomba kwirinda ko amazi yo mu ntoki asubira mu biganza.
Iyo bamaze gukaraba intoki, intoki zabo ziba zimeshejwe umwenda utuma umuntu atagira inda, maze bakambara ikanzu y'ubuvuzi.
Kugira ngo indwara zidakwirakwira cyane, ni byiza koza intoki cyangwa gukoresha umuti wo kuzirinda indwara mbere y'uko ugiye kwita ku murwayi cyangwa nyuma yaho.
Mu kurwanya indwara z'ibicurane mu bitaro, byagaragariye ko inyungu ikomeye kurusha izindi zo gukaraba intoki zavuye ku 20% z'imyitozo ya mbere, kandi ko inyungu z'inyongera zari nke cyane igihe imihango yo gukaraba intoki yarushagaho kwiyongeraho 35%.
Gukoresha isabune isanzwe bituma indwara zandurira mu mikorobe zandura mu biribwa zigera kuri gatatu ugereranyije no gukoreshwa isabune yo kurwanya za bagiteri. Gupereranya gukoreshwa isabune yo gukaraba intoki n'umuti ushyigikiwe na alkoholi hamwe no gukoreshwa isabune yo gukaraba intoki mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30 buri gihe byagaragaje ko gukoresha isabune yo gukaraba intoki yabaga ikoresheje inzoga byagabanyije kwandura kwa bagiteriyo ku kigero cya 26% kurusha isabune yo kurwanya za bagiteriyo.
Ariko isabune n'amazi birusha neza imyenda y'intoki ishingiye ku nzoga kugabanya virusi ya H1N1 y'ibicurane A n'ibitero bya Clostridium difficile mu ntoki.Ibikorwa byo kunoza isuku y'intoki mu by'ubuzima bishobora gusaba ko abakozi bigishwa uko bakaraba intoki, bakongera umubare w'imyenda y'intoki ishingiye ku nzoga, ndetse n'ibyibutsa byanditse n'ibyavuzwe ku bakozi.
Hakenewe gukorwa ubushakashatsi kurushaho kugira ngo hagaragazwe uburyo bwo kuvura bwo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi bufite akamaro kurusha ubundi.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, gukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune birazwi ko ari uburyo bw'ingenzi bufite agaciro kandi bufite akamaro cyane kugira ngo umuntu agire ubuzima bwiza, ndetse akagira n'imirire myiza.
Icyakora, kubera ko abantu badafite amazi meza, isabune cyangwa ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu ngo zabo, mu mashuri no ku kazi, kubona uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki mu rwego rw'isi yose birabagoye.
Urugero, mu turere twinshi two muri Afurika, nta mazu yo gukaraba intoki aba hafi y'aho umuntu yiyuhagira cyangwa aho aba ari hose, nubwo hari uburyo bworoheje bwo kubaka ahantu ho gukaraba intoki.
Icyakora, kuba abantu bakoresha amazi meza mu gihe bakoresha amazi meza, bishobora guterwa n'uko hari abantu benshi bafite akamenyero ko gukora nabi.
Gushyigikira no guteza imbere gukaraba intoki n'isabune bishobora kugira ingaruka ku myanzuro ya politiki, bigatuma abantu bamenya akamaro ko gukaraba intoki kandi bigatuma abaturage bagira ihinduka mu myifatire yabo mu gihe kirekire.
Kugira ngo ibyo bikore neza, ni ngombwa ko hagenzurwa kandi hagatangwa ingero.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bushakashatsi 70 bwagaragaje ko uburyo bushingiye ku muryango bushobora gutuma imikoreshereze yo gukaraba intoki mu bigo by'amashuri by'inganda bikoresha ikoranabuhanga riganje mu gihugu, mu gihe ubukangurambaga bwo kwamamaza mu rwego rw'ubucuruzi bushobora gutuma imikoreshereze y'ubucuruzi ikoreshwa mu mashuri ikoreshwa nabi.
Iyo amahame y'ibanze agera ku rwego rwo hasi, amashuri ashobora kuva ku nyenyeri imwe agera ku nyenyeri eshatu.
Kubaka ahantu ho gukaraba intoki bishobora kuba kimwe mu bigize gahunda zo kwamamaza gukaraba intoki zigamije kugabanya indwara n'ubwandu bw'abana.
Umunsi mpuzamahanga wo gukaraba intoki ni urugero rw'ubukangurambaga bwo kumenyekanisha ibikorwa byo guhindura imyitwarire.Mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya Coronavirus cya 2019-20, UNICEF yashishikarije abantu gukoresha imvugo yo gukaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi buke bwakozwe bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere mu buryo buhuje n'uko ibipimo by'ubuvuzi by'ibiyobyabwenge by'ubuvuzi byirindwa.
Icyakora, hari ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gushyigikira gukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune, bituma amafaranga menshi ugura kurusha andi mahitamo yo gukoresha amazi n'isuku.
Impamvu yo gukaraba intoki ku buzima bw'abantu  by'umwihariko ku bantu bari mu mimerere itoroshye, urugero nk'ababyeyi bari bamaze kubyara cyangwa abasirikare bakomeretse mu bitaro  byatangiye kumenyekana mu kinyejana cya 19 hagati n'abahanga babiri mu birebana no kwirinda indwara z'ibibembe: umuganga Ignaz Semmelweis wo muri Hongiriya wakoreraga i Vienne muri Otirishiya na Florence Nightingale, "wabanje kwita ku buvuzi bwa none" mu Bwongereza.
Icyo gihe abantu benshi bari bakiremera ko indwara ziterwa n'impumuro mbi ziswe miasma.
Mu myaka ya 1980, indwara zandurira mu biribwa n'izindi ndwara zifitanye isano n'ubuzima byatumye Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyita ku isuku y'amaboko mu buryo bw'ingenzi kugira ngo kizibuze kwandura.
Icyorezo cya Grippe y'Ingurube mu 2009 n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu 2020 byatumye abantu benshi bo mu bihugu byinshi barushaho kumenya akamaro ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune kugira ngo umuntu arinde indwara zandura.
Urugero, hari ibyapa byari bifite "uburyo bukwiriye bwo gukaraba intoki" byashyizwe iruhande rw'ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu bwiherero rusange no mu bwiherero bw'amazu y'ibiro n'ibibuga by'indege byo mu Budage.
Imvugo ngo "kwambika umuntu ibiganza" yumvikanisha ko umuntu atifuza kwifatira uwo murimo cyangwa ko ari we ubikora.
Ryaturutse mu gice cyo muri Bibiliya cya Matayo aho Ponsiyo Pilato yahanaguye umwanzuro wo kubamba Yesu Kristo, ariko ryahindutse imvugo ikoreshwa mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe byo mu Bwongereza.
Mu gitabo cya Shakespeare cyitwa Macbeth, Lady Macbeth atangira gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'agahato mu kugerageza guhanagura icyuma cy'ibyiyumvo, agaragaza ko afite umutimanama wicira urubanza ku byaha yakoze kandi akaba yarashishikarije umugabo we gukora.
Nanone kandi, byagiye bigaragara ko abantu bamaze kwibuka cyangwa gutekereza ku bikorwa bidahuje n'amahame mbwirizamuco, bakunda gukaraba intoki kenshi kurusha abandi, kandi bakunda guha agaciro ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki.
Byongeye kandi, abantu bemerewe gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gutekereza batyo, ntibashobora gukora ibindi bikorwa byo "kugira isuku", urugero nko gukora imirimo y'ubwitange.
Amadini atuma abantu bakaraba intoki haba mu rwego rw'isuku ndetse no mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo. Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo, hakoreshejwe amazi ariko nta sabuni yo gukaraba intoki, ni kimwe mu bigize imihango yo gukaraba intoki mu madini menshi, harimo Ukwizera kwa Bahá'í, idini ry'Abahindw'i, tevilah na netilat yadayim mu idini ry'Abayahudi, Lavabo mu Bukristo, na Wudhu mu idini rya Isilamu. Amadini na yo atuma abantu bakaraba intoki mu buryo bw'isuku, cyane cyane nyuma y'ibikorwa bimwe na bimwe.
Abahindu, Abayahudi n'Abisilamu bategeka ko umuntu akaraba intoki nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero.
Kandi, idini ry'Abahindu, ry'Ababuda, ry'Abasikishi, ry'Abayahudi n'irya Isilamu, ritegeka ko umuntu akaraba intoki mbere y'uko arya cyangwa nyuma y'icyo arya.
Ibikorwa byo kugenzura ibyago byo kurwara COVID-19 mu kazi
Gukurikirana ibyago ku kazi kubera COVID-19 ni ugushyira mu bikorwa uburyo bwo kwirinda impanuka mu kazi no kugenzura ubuzima mu kwirinda icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Kugenzura ibyago mu kazi ku buryo bukwiriye, biva ku kazi n'akazi, bishingiye ku isuzuma ry'ibyago byo kwandura, ubukana bw'indwara mu baturage, n'ibimenyetso by'ibyago by'abakozi bashobora kwandura COVID-19.
Ikigo gishinzwe umutekano n'ubuzima ku kazi muri Amerika (OSHA), kivuga ko imirimo idahungabanya ubuzima bw'abantu ku kazi, nta cyo ihuriyeho n'abandi bakozi, kandi ko bagombye gukurikiza ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda indwara, urugero nko gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, kwirinda guhumeka no gukora isuku no guhumanya indwara mu kazi.
Imirimo irimo ibyago byo kubura ubwandu bw'ibiyobyabwenge harimo iyo bisaba guhura kenshi cyangwa guhuza n'abantu batazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura kubera ikwirakwira ry'abaturage cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Ibyo bikubiyemo abakozi bafitanye isano n'abantu benshi, urugero nk'amashuri, ahantu ho gukorera abantu benshi, ndetse n'aho bakorera ibicuruzwa byinshi.
Ibikoresho byo kugenzura akaga kuri iri tsinda, uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura, birimo guhumeka hakoreshejwe ibigega by'umwuka bifite ubushobozi buhambaye, abirinda guhumeka, no kugira ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku giti cyawe mu gihe umuntu urwaye COVID-19 abonye.
OSHA ifata abakozi b'ubuzima n'abajyanama b'abapfuye bashyizwe mu bikorwa n'umuntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho kuba afite COVID-19 nk'abafite ibyago byinshi byo gushyirwa mu bikorwa, ibyo bikaba byongera bigatuma umuntu agira ibyago byinshi cyane iyo abakozi bakoze imikorere ituma habaho umuti wa Aerosol, cyangwa bakusanya cyangwa bagakora ibipimo by'umuntu uzwi cyangwa ukekwaho kuba afite COVID-19.
Mu byo kugenzura akaga bikwiye ku bakozi, harimo kugenzura ingufu nk'ibyumba byo guhumeka bihamye, n'ibikoresho by'uburinzi bwite bikwiye gukora akazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka zitandukanye mu kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kuba batari ku kazi kubera ko barwaye, ko bagomba kwita ku bandi cyangwa kubera gutinya ko bashobora guhura n'indwara.
Imiterere y'ubucuruzi ishobora guhinduka, haba mu bihereranye n'ibyo bicuruzwa bifuza, ndetse n'uburyo bwo kugura ibicuruzwa (nk'urugero rwo kugura mu masaha y'ikirenga cyangwa binyuze mu gutanga cyangwa gutwara imodoka).
Amaherezo, ibicuruzwa byo mu duce two mu karere kahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye za COVID-19 bishobora guhagarikwa.
Ibi bikorwa by'ubuyobozi bw'akarere ka Musanze byashyizweho mu rwego rwo guhangana n'ibibazo by'ubukene n'uburwayi.
Nanone kandi, zigaragaza uburyo bwo kugenzura ibyo bibazo n'imigambi y'ubutabazi ku bibazo bishobora guterwa n'ibyago.
Imigambi yo kwitegura indwara zandura no guhangana na zo ishobora gukurikizwa mu rwego rw'igihugu cyangwa mu rwego rw'igihugu.
Mu ntego zo guhangana n'icyorezo harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira hagati y'abakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kugira ibibazo by'ubuzima bidakwiriye, gukomeza ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku zindi nzego ziri mu nzego z'ubucuruzi.
Uburemere bw'indwara mu gace uwo mushinga ukoreramo, bugira ingaruka ku byo umuntu akora.
Ikirere cy'ibiza ni uburyo bwakoreshejwe cyane mu bijyanye n'umutekano n'ubuzima mu kazi kugira ngo abantu bashyiremo ingufu mu gucunga ibiza.
Aho hatari ya COVID-19 idashobora kuvanwaho, uburyo bwiza bwo kugenzura ni ubugenzuzi bw'ubuhanga, bukurikirwa n'ubugenzuzi bw'ubuyobozi, hanyuma bukarimburwa n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi.
Ubuyobozi bw'ubuhanga bukora ibyo guhana abakozi ku kaga gaterwa n'akazi, nta gushingira ku myitwarire y'abakozi, kandi bushobora kuba uburyo bw'ingirakamaro cyane bwo gushyira mu bikorwa.
Igenzura ry'ubuyobozi ni ihinduka mu politiki y'akazi cyangwa mu mikorere isaba ko umukozi cyangwa umukoresha agira icyo akora.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku giti cyawe (PPE) bifatwa ko bidafite akamaro kurusha ibikoresho by'ubugenzuzi n'ubuyobozi, ariko bishobora gufasha kwirinda bimwe mu bintu bishobora gutuma umuntu agaragara.
Ubwoko bwose bw'Ibikoresho by'Umutekano w'Umubiri (PPE) bugomba gutorwa hashingiwe ku kaga kagarije umukozi, bugashyirwa mu buryo bukwiriye nk'uko bikwiye (urugero, ibyuma bihumeka), bugakoreshwa neza kandi mu buryo bukwiriye, bugasuzumwa buri gihe, bugakorwaho imirimo, bugasimburwa, uko bikenewe, kandi bukurwaho neza, bugasukuzwa, bukabikwa cyangwa bukicwa kugira ngo butagwa mu ndwara.
Ikigo gishinzwe umutekano n'ubuzima ku kazi muri Amerika (OSHA), kivuga ko imirimo idahungabanya ubuzima bw'abantu ku kazi, nta mishyikirano ihambaye iba ifitanye n'abantu benshi n'abandi bakozi.
Mu ngamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura zasabwe ku kazi kose harimo gukaraba intoki kenshi kandi mu buryo bunonosoye, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, kwirinda guhumeka, harimo no guhisha ububabare no guhumeka, gutanga imyenda n'ibikoresho by'ubutayu, kwitegura gukora imirimo ya kure cyangwa imirimo y'akazi mu gihe bibaye ngombwa, guca intege abakozi ngo batakoresha ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'abandi, no gukomeza gukora isuku n'ubwandu bw'ibikorwaruhiro.
Gushakisha abantu bashobora kwandura vuba no kubashyira mu kato ni intambwe y'ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi mu kazi.
Ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitanga inama y'uko abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara ikomeye yo mu buryo bw'ubuhumekero bagomba kuguma mu rugo kugeza igihe bazaba batagaragaje umuriro, ibimenyetso by'umuriro n'indi mibonera mibi nibura amasaha 24 badafite imiti igabanya umuriro cyangwa izindi ndwara zihindura ibimenyetso, kandi ko gahunda z'ikiruhuko cyo kurwara zifite ubushobozi bwo guhinduka, zigatuma abakozi bashobora kuguma mu rugo kugira ngo bita ku muntu urwaye mu muryango, kandi ko abakozi bazi izo gahunda.
