Interleukin-6 receptor antagonist yemewe na FDA ishingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe nyuma mu gihe cyo kuvura indwara ya stéroïdes zitukura cytokine zituruka ku mpamvu zitandukanye, ubuvuzi bw'ingirabuzimafatizo za CAR T, mu 2017.
Kugeza ubu, nta bimenyetso byagenwe ku buryo bw'impanuka byemeza ko tocilizumab ari umuti ugira ingaruka nziza ku CRS.
Gushyiraho imiti y'ubwirinzi ikoreshwa n'abakize COVID-19 ikoreshwa mu kurwanya indwara z'uburwayi, ikoreshwa mu gukingira abantu bakenera imiti, birimo gukorwaho iperereza nk'uburyo bw'ubwirinzi butari bwo gukingira.
Iyi nzira yageragejwe mu kurwanya SARS ariko nta cyo yabashije kugeraho.
Kwifata ku ngufu ni uburyo bwitezwe bwo gukora, ubwo imiti y'inyamaswa ikora ku mubiri ishobora gutuma umuntu arwanya SARS-CoV-2.
Icyakora, hari izindi ngamba zishobora kubaho, urugero nko gutwara uturemangingo tw'ingirabuzimafatizo tw'ibinyabuzima bikorera ku mubiri n'/cyangwa gutwara uturemangingo tw'ibinyabuzima (phagocytosis).
Hari ubundi buryo bwo kuvura umubiri, urugero nko gukoresha imiti y'umubiri umwe, biri gukorwa.
Kugira ngo iki cyorezo kiboneke vuba, bishobora kongera ubushobozi bwo gukora serum yo kuvura, igizwe n'igice cy'amaraso cy'abarwayi bakize, kandi kirimo uturemangingo tumwe na tumwe tumwe tumenyekanira kuri iyi virusi.
